---
title: Fattoush-Inspired Chicken Breasts Salad with Spiced Flatbreads and Feta Cheese
description: Everything about this salad delights! Our take on this Mediterranean dish is layered with roasted garlic dressing, fresh herbs and veggies, chicken, crispy chickpeas and flavourful, crunchy flatbread.
